      "originalText": {
        "text": "This a main healthcare poin  in Ulcinj. They offer healthcare service for locals but also for tourist. Mostly you will get help here very fast. For some most serious cases you will be ask to go to Hospital in Bar. Staff is mostly friendly even they have lots to do.",
